This work seeks to extend a company‘s systems to the reach of its mobile on-field staff bringing them into the umbrella of users benefited by the use of technology. The MSales project is cantered on bringing into being a unique portable device/mobile application that will simplify and lesson the work of sales and delivery persons by incorporating technology to aid their activities, thereby, essentially maximising the productivity, efficiency and flexibility of the company‘s sales department by enabling user friendly, real time cost effective, scalable data collection and management on the mobile phone.
